{
  "stem": "17526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Its council and its committees and everything was run according to the rules and regulations prevailing at the time and in accordance with the Polish regulations, naturally.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We may not have felt the anti-Semites right on the street where we lived because it was all Jewish people, but as soon as you ventured outside of the outskirts of the city, you could not miss the point that anti-Semitism is prevailing and so forth and so on.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like for instance, in the summertime when we would take trips out of town, we'd hire these-- the organization would take us out for outings, picnics.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would be stoned on the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was a natural thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would have been surprised if it wasn't the case.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in many cases, we fought back but it was a fact of life that we lived with.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you just couldn't not notice it and you couldn't avoid it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1939, right from the very beginning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the war first broke out, things were turned upside-down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we still did not realize how much-- how what we are entering.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't anticipate it because it was just unbelievable that these things would happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, there were too many rumors flying around and nothing could be substantiated, but we knew that the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And two days later, the next day, we saw the German front tanks marching through our streets due to the fact that our street was so close to the German border and this happened to have been one of the main thoroughfares.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right the street where I was born and raised, right in front of the house, they were coming from-- from the west, marching east.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
